channel.title: Go Baby Go Spokane!
channel.description: We want to share that we have a chapter in Spokane, WA, that serves Eastern WA and Northern ID. We have a minimum of twice-yearly builds and monthly playgroups at ParaSport Spokane. We can be reached at gbgspokane@gmail.com and are on Facebook; Go Baby Go Spokane. Thanks!
